{"tid":1225951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣有舖頭個老細話示威者俾人開槍射都係抵佢死！！","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:30:13.000Z","uid":69746,"like":1339,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbbb6f819221248fa8dfcc7929b7a1810e2cebd","tid":1225951,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"話說荃灣有間賣運動用品嘅鋪頭叫中x，呢間叫x興嘅運動用品舖我細個成日去買嘢因為學校有時有折 <br />\n但係我今日去嗰度買嘢嗰陣聽到個仆街老細講 ，啲示威者咁樣擾亂社會秩序俾人開槍射都係抵死，萬一死左都唔好怨！就連啲店員都好似係咁諗！<br />\n我聽到嬲到即刻走咗。我以後都唔會幫襯佢 大家快啲一齊抵制呢啲仆街黑店<br />\n呢間黑店好似警犬買嘢會計平好多，呢啲仆街到咁撚樣嘅黑店真係要推到佢收皮至得<br />\n<br />\n利申:發緊夢"},{"pid":"985ebb55ef4bf387ae504ecf733fde2b748e60ee","tid":1225951,"uid":198035,"like":17,"dislike":601,"score":-584,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁你就開全名啦"},{"pid":"ad5c7bc8ec56ddab7d7433565631b754d884acca","tid":1225951,"uid":214446,"like":8,"dislike":352,"score":-344,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"83ec3cadb628036f34d27732c5aaf65f17ae9d71","tid":1225951,"uid":119591,"like":373,"dislike":0,"score":373,"quote":{"pid":"985ebb55ef4bf387ae504ecf733fde2b748e60ee","tid":1225951,"uid":198035,"like":17,"dislike":601,"score":-584,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁你就開全名啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f374e8bac7d7a012cf44c53bc66fbe70c6cbf05","tid":1225951,"uid":197813,"like":283,"dislike":0,"score":283,"quote":{"pid":"ad5c7bc8ec56ddab7d7433565631b754d884acca","tid":1225951,"uid":214446,"like":8,"dislike":352,"score":-344,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"咪開咗...."},{"pid":"c16c59846fee78b0229e8f9d806e33e6318661be","tid":1225951,"uid":123875,"like":235,"dislike":2,"score":233,"quote":{"pid":"985ebb55ef4bf387ae504ecf733fde2b748e60ee","t